msg.msgText: A call to nextElement() on a QueueBrowser's Enumeration object failed because there are no more elements to be browsed.

msgExplanation.p: When there are no remaining elements in a QueueBrowser's Enumeration object, a call to nextElement() causes NoSuchElementException.

msgUserResponse.p: None. NoSuchElementException indicates that the end of the data was reached. However, to avoid the exception, you can call hasMoreElements() before calling nextElement().
